--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
I: improvement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.1.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 2.0.0 (2018-02-20)
I: Simplify and improve Ansible role

* Version 1.2.0 (2017-10-18)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.2
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.1

* Version 1.1.0 (2017-08-26)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.1-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE

* Version 1.0.0 (2017-08-01)
I: Stabilize, improve and cleanup Ansible role

* Version 0.5.0 (2017-04-16)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.1
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.0

* Version 0.4.0 (2016-10-14)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE

* Version 0.3.0 (2016-09-03)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.0
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 5.9

* Version 0.2.2 (2016-05-29)
I: Improve FreeBSD support

* Version 0.2.1 (2016-05-27)
I: Improve packaging tasks

* Version 0.2.0 (2016-05-21)
F: Add support for Ansible 2.0

* Version 0.1.0 (2016-04-18)
F: Initial release
